title: History Extra podcast - September 2009 - Part 2
itunes:title: History Extra podcast - September 2009 - Part 2
itunes:subtitle: This month Dan Snow gives his opinions on the momentous Battle of Quebec that took place 250 years ago. Plus we speak to Tracy Borman about how Elizabeth I grew envious of the other women at her court.
